# SERVICE SCOPE (Device Controller Service - C++)

## Service is a hardware control PLATFORM
- No UI/UX logic
- No session/business/policy logic
- No dependence on Flutter

## Service owns
- device control (camera/printer/payment)
- device state machines
- recovery (reconnect/backoff/hung detection)
- IPC command handling + event streaming + state snapshots
- logging/telemetry for operations

## Service must NOT
- generate collage images
- interpret app layouts or prompts
- decide customer flow